{
  "id": "6a1c095046b063ecb9579d0b",
  "title": "日本綜合論",
  "created": 1780222291,
  "updated": 1780224295,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a1c095046b063ecb9579d0b",
      "text": "日本綜合論",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780222291,
      "updated": 1780222291
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c102b0000000000244f26",
      "text": "[デライト.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1780224044,
      "updated": 1780224051
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0933000000000066dd6c",
      "text": " [イギリス経験論]、[大陸合理論]、[ドイツ観念論]後の統一的な思想体系として[日本]で再構築された[新現代思想][hiro.icon]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780222291,
      "updated": 1780223557
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0abf000000000066dd6e",
      "text": "  英：Japanese Synthetism",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780222687,
      "updated": 1780222699
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0e4d000000000066dd7b",
      "text": "  日本の思想的伝統を「綜合」（synthesis）とし、それを積極的に活かしていく",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223597,
      "updated": 1780223765
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0c20000000000066dd73",
      "text": "  その原点は[聖徳太子]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223040,
      "updated": 1780223052
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0c2d000000000066dd74",
      "text": "   日本人としていわゆる[和の思想]を最初に唱えた人物",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223054,
      "updated": 1780223246
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0cf1000000000066dd76",
      "text": "   [中村元]によれば日本最初の思想家",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223249,
      "updated": 1780223328
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0d40000000000066dd77",
      "text": "  [空海]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223328,
      "updated": 1780223392
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0d84000000000066dd78",
      "text": "   [綜芸種智院]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223396,
      "updated": 1780223432
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c11020000000000d1ea6c",
      "text": "  [南方熊楠]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780224291,
      "updated": 1780224295
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c10990000000000d1ea69",
      "text": "  [京都学派]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780224186,
      "updated": 1780224190
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c104e0000000000d1ea68",
      "text": "   [和辻哲郎]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780224110,
      "updated": 1780224192
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0da9000000000066dd79",
      "text": "   [西田幾多郎]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223433,
      "updated": 1780224193
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0b6f000000000066dd70",
      "text": "    西洋思想と東洋思想の統合",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780222864,
      "updated": 1780224194
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c10c50000000000d1ea6a",
      "text": "  [井筒俊彦]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780224229,
      "updated": 1780224234
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c10ec0000000000d1ea6b",
      "text": "  [中村元]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780224268,
      "updated": 1780224274
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0f30000000000066dd7c",
      "text": "  [希哲館事業]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223824,
      "updated": 1780223828
    },
    {
      "id": "6a1c0f31000000000066dd7d",
      "text": "   [ジパング計画]",
      "userId": "5f11a68e5fc065001ecf5795",
      "created": 1780223826,
      "updated": 1780223836
    },
    {
